<http://purl.org/heritagedata/schemes/1/concepts/54>	"RIG AND FURROW"@en
<http://purl.org/heritagedata/schemes/1/concepts/503820>	"WATERCRESS BED"@en


# list all the properties of this particular collection
DESCRIBE <http://purl.org/heritagedata/schemes/1/collections/C100>

Results:
@prefix rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
